| `home` | `/` | `src/app/page.tsx` | No | Buyer dashboard homepage (Figma node `798:6035`). Top Brands, New Releases, Fish Type categories, Favorites, Promo CTAs, Brand Suggestions, Because You Like. |
| `login` | `/login` | `src/app/login/page.tsx` | No | Email/password sign-in and sign-up. Redirects to `/create-listing` on success. |
| `shop` | `/shop` | — | No | Shop (placeholder) |
