| `map` | `/map` | — | No | Map (placeholder) |
| `profile` | `/profile` | `src/app/profile/page.tsx` | No | Profile (Figma node `772:2307`). Avatar, display name, Edit, username, location, "Add some information" CTA, QR + follower link, section TabsBox (Order, Favorites, Comments, Settings), content Tabs (My videos, Tagged, etc.), empty video state. Edit navigates to `/settings/account`. |
