| `listingDetail(id)` | `/listings/[id]` | `src/app/listings/[id]/page.tsx` | No | Listing detail page. Shows product image, title, price, condition, category, description, seller info, variant selection with stock display, cost breakdown, and Buy Now button that initiates Stripe Checkout. |
| `checkoutSuccess` | `/checkout/success` | `src/app/checkout/success/page.tsx` | No | Post-checkout confirmation page. Shows success message after Stripe redirects back with `?session_id=`. |
| `stripeConnectReturn` | `/stripe/connect/return` | `src/app/stripe/connect/return/page.tsx` | No | Stripe Connect onboarding return page. Checks verification status and shows success/pending message. |
